'Any chance to add more Huy Fong Sriracha Hot Sauce is a good thing. 

'And it pairs so well with other spicy foods, like soups, sauces, hamburgers, pizza, chow mein and so on.

'It tastes like someone used Huy Fong Sriracha Hot Sauce while brewing a stout.

'The beer has been met by some excitement and some confusion, but everyone's intrigued. True Huy Fong sriracha sauce fans seem to like it.' 

The independent brewery prides itself on handcrafted ales, porters, stouts, lagers and spirits. 

On its website the makers state: 'The spirit of the Rogue brand, even the name, suggests doing things differently, a desire and a willingness to change the status quo. 

'A Rogue ale, porter, stout, lager or spirit is crafted to give it unique character, innovative in its make-up and brewing a process that has not compromised quality.

'We make products for the connoisseur, the entrepreneur and the revolutionist.' 

 

